  "description": "This individual is a compact, broad-shouldered woman with bronze skin and brown eyes set beneath heavy, work-worn brows. Black hair is kept in a practical ponytail, exposing a square jaw and a nose flattened by long-ago impacts. Fine pitting scars on the knuckles and a network of shallow burn marks along the forearms mark years of contact with hot metal, harsh spirits, and chemical cleaners. Her face carries deepened smile lines that read as practiced hospitality rather than softness.",
